p: A total of 240 randomly selected acute serum specimens (172 from 2016, 68 from 2017) sent to RCDC were tested for serotype identification by DENV nested RT-PCR and 160 (67%) were positive ( S2 Table). Serotype identification for 160 PCR positive samples revealed 117 DENV-1 (93 in 2016 and 24 in 2017) and 43 DENV-2 (37 in 2016 and 6 in 2017).
